50|$|Recognized both by Tibetan Buddhists and {{by other}} spiritual {{practitioners}} and scholars as a preeminent teacher <b>of</b> Tibetan <b>Buddhism,</b> {{he was a}} major figure in the dissemination <b>of</b> Tibetan <b>Buddhism</b> to the West, founding Vajradhatu and Naropa University and establishing the Shambhala Training method.|$|R
